We are a leading provider of innovative outdoor products that enable our customers to achieve rugged independence in the activity of their choice. Vista Outdoor operates in two primary business segments: Shooting Sports and Outdoor Products. Our portfolio includes well-respected brands designed to bring the world outside. Our highly recognized brands include Federal Premium®, CamelBak®, Savage Arms™, Bushnell®, Primos®, BLACKHAWK!®, Bollé®, Bell, Giro and many others.
