Stock Price
NYSE:VSTO
$23.13

$(0.26)
        
Volume : 543,344
As of July 28, 2017 CloseMinimum 20 minute delay.






















                          
                          Vista Outdoor is a leading global designer, manufacturer and marketer of consumer 
products in the growing outdoor sports and recreation markets.

Our portfolio offers consumers a range of performance-driven, 
high-quality and innovative products.

Our business strategy is to deliver long-term shareholder value by:

• Leveraging our engineering, sourcing, sales, marketing and distribution capabilities 
to create a broad portfolio for the outdoor enthusiast
• Growing our brands and expanding into complementary and adjacent markets
• Focusing on execution excellence and efficiency in all aspects of our business

Our company serves a broad range of consumers – from hunters and recreational shooters 
to golfers and skiers to law enforcement and military professionals. We make sporting 
ammunition, firearms, outdoor products, personal hydration solutions, sports optics, golf rangefinders, 
performance eyewear, action sports helmets and goggles, footwear and a variety 
of cycling accessories, stand up paddle boards and accessories. 

We're passionate about these products because our employees use these products. 
We understand what our customers need to achieve independence and success. 




