… Combined with Disciplined Approach to Valuation




Invest only in companies that present attractive opportunities for Vista Outdoor to leverage its sales force, operating expertise and strategic guidance to create value
Ensure all acquisition multiples can be supported by comparable market transaction(s), cash flow models and return thresholds
Utilize creative transaction structures to align incentives, while remaining disciplined on price
Opportunistically approach owners to avoid auction processes





